        <updateDate>2007-03-20T20:07:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends title XXI (State Children's Health Insurance) (SCHIP) of the Social Security Act to require the Secretary of Health and Human Services to apply specified rules for an additional redistribution of amounts from unexpended FY2005-FY2006 allotments to address funding shortfalls in SCHIP for FY2007.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
